Hi nfoscarini ,

those "X" links are speculative links found by the JavaScript 
Link-Extractor (Or maybe even caused be AggressiveExtractorHTML).
Scroll down to the bottom of your websites source code and you will find 
something like:

{ coded = "wOGq0Z@..."

This is what caused this false positive.

Regards
   Olaf Freyer
